<p>Losing a friend is a heartbreaking experience.  Your words of comfort can make a difference in their journey through grief. Offer these expressions of sympathy:</p>
<li>I am so incredibly sorry to hear about your loss.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you during this difficult time.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you as you grieve the loss of your dear friend.</li>
<li>Remembering [friend's name] with fondness and love.</li>
<li>You are not alone in your sorrow.</li>
<li> [Friend's name] was such a special person.</li>
<li>I will cherish the memories we shared with [friend's name].</li>
<li>I am here for you, whatever you may need.</li>
<li>Sending you much love and support.</li>
<li>Your friendship with [friend's name] was truly special.</li>
<li>May the happy memories you shared bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Please reach out if you need anything at all.</li>
